snippet.title: Why Does Mera Have An ACCENT In Zack Snyder's Justice League?
snippet.description:
So Amber Heard's Mera has a British accent in Zack Synder's Justice League. Even though she never had it before, which doesn't really make any sense. So why? Let me know what you think and make sure to subscribe to the channel for more content!! #Mera #ZackSyndersJusticeLeague #AmberHeard
